"registered organization" means a registered organization within the meaning
of Division 8A of Part III of the Assessment Act;
  "resident beneficiary", in relation to a year of income, means a beneficiary
of a trust estate who is not a prescribed non-resident in relation to that
year of income;
  "resident taxpayer", in relation to a year of income, means a taxpayer who
is not a prescribed non-resident in relation to that year of income;
  "resident trust estate", in relation to a year of income, means a trust
estate that, under sub-section 95 (2) of the Assessment Act, is to be taken to
be a resident trust estate in relation to that year of income;
